snippet.title: Transformers Rescue Bots : Disaster Dash | Google Play Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Download on the Google Play Store: 
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.budgestudios.googleplay.TransformersDisasterDash

Budge Studios™ presents Transformers Rescue Bots: Disaster Dash!

Assemble all the Rescue Bots and go on an action-packed adventure to save the world from the evil Dr. Morocco! Rescue citizens, outrun disasters and chase down Morbots. Avoid obstacles, collect Energon and morph from bot to vehicle to epic DinoBot! 

Roll to the rescue!

Like us on Facebook ! www.facebook.com/budgestudios
